35
00:04:01,320 --> 00:04:02,640
Mom is dying!

36
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:05,680
Ling Xiao!

37
00:04:08,280 --> 00:04:09,240
Ling Xiao!

38
00:04:11,160 --> 00:04:12,840
Hurry up!

39
00:04:15,200 --> 00:04:15,680
Mom!

40
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:16,390
Doctor!

41
00:04:16,390 --> 00:04:17,800
Mom!

42
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:21,800
Mom! Mom! Mom!

43
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:23,960
Grandma! Grandma!

44
00:04:23,960 --> 00:04:26,320
Mom!

45
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:28,160
Grandma!

46
