so many things?

115
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:39,800
He has grown up

116
00:07:40,159 --> 00:07:41,000
and he has to

117
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:42,080
handle it

118
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:43,460
no matter what.

119
00:07:44,200 --> 00:07:45,680
How did it happen?

120
00:07:47,720 --> 00:07:48,600
He drove

121
