151
00:09:43,760 --> 00:09:44,720
the green bean soup

152
00:09:44,720 --> 00:09:46,180
that Jianjian made for me.

153
00:09:46,880 --> 00:09:47,440
Come.

154
00:09:47,680 --> 00:09:48,640
Please have some fruits.

155
00:09:48,640 --> 00:09:49,480
Please have some fruits.

156
