Ziqiu,

158
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:53,200
go and make a cup for your dad.

159
00:09:53,200 --> 00:09:53,680
OK.

160
00:09:55,960 --> 00:09:57,840
Thank you very much.

161
00:09:58,520 --> 00:09:59,280
Thank you

162
00:09:59,280 --> 00:10:00,520
for coming to see me.

163
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:01,960
We're

164
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:02,960
just fine.

165
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:07,320
We work in the neighborhood committee

166
00:10:07,440 --> 00:10:08,370
and it's our duty

167
00:10:08,760 --> 00:10:09,920
to show loving care

168
00:10:09,920 --> 00:10:11,120
for every household.

169
00:10:12,280 --> 00:10:14,360
How miserable it is!

170
00:10:14,440 --> 00:10:15,680
Mrs. Chen

171
00:10:15,760 --> 00:10:17,400
was not very old,

172
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:19,480
but she was an old person,

173
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:22,280
but Chen Ting is still young

174
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:24,760
and her daughter is still so little.

175
00:10:24,760 --> 00:10:26,520
If she can't make it,

176
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:28,090
it'll be such a pity.

177
00:10:28,400 --> 00:10:30,530
But there's nothing we can do about it.

178
00:10:30,920 --> 00:10:33,160
People die when it's time.

179
00:10:33,280 --> 00:10:34,600
And it's

180
00:10:34,800 --> 00:10:35,840
all predestined.

181
00:10:36,960 --> 00:10:37,840
Well,

182
00:10:39,160 --> 00:10:40,440
it's so hard

183
00:10:40,640 --> 00:10:41,640
for Ling Xiao.

184
00:10:41,880 --> 00:10:42,720
Yes.

185
00:10:43,240 --> 00:10:43,600
By the way,

186
00:10:43,600 --> 00:10:44,860
has he gone over there?

187
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:45,680
Yes.

188
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:48,520
He went over there with his uncle

189
00:10:48,680 --> 00:10:50,680
from his grandma's home yesterday.

190
00:10:51,120 --> 00:10:52,480
In all of these years,

191
00:10:52,680 --> 00:10:54,740
Chen Ting has never taken care of him,

192
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:56,360
but when something is up,

193
00:10:56,360 --> 00:10:57,840
Ling Xiao will still

194
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:59,290
take care of his mother.

195
00:10:59,800 --> 00:11:01,360
And Ziqiu's mother,

196
00:11:01,960 --> 00:11:03,680
if something happens to her in the future,

197
00:11:03,680 --> 00:11:05,140
she will come to Ziqiu too.

198
00:11:10,720 --> 00:11:12,160
Have some tea, please.

199
00:11:12,600 --> 00:11:13,440
OK. OK.

200
00:11:20,960 --> 00:11:21,640
Good one!

201
00:11:49,800 --> 00:11:51,130
How is it going with you?

202
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:53,520
Not bad.

203
00:11:54,120 --> 00:11:55,720
My goal is Wuhan University,

204
00:11:56,040 --> 00:11:57,440
but if the admission score is the same as last year,

205
00:11:57,440 --> 00:11:58,280
I might fail

206
00:11:58,600 --> 00:12:00,530
and I'll consider other colleges.

207
00:12:01,120 --> 00:12:01,980
What about you?

208
00:12:03,640 --> 00:12:04,370
I don't know.

209
00:12:06,240 --> 00:12:07,900
I haven't asked Ling Xiao yet.

210
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:08,560
It's fine.

211
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:10,120
As long as you two

212
00:12:10,120 --> 00:12:11,360
are in the same city.

213
00:12:15,760 --> 00:12:16,840
What do you say

214
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:19,600
if I study abroad

215
00:12:19,760 --> 00:12:21,280
and take a year of preparatory course?

216
00:12:21,280 --> 00:12:22,840
I completely agree!

217
00:12:24,320 --> 00:12:25,280
Would you go

218
00:12:25,280 --> 00:12:26,080
if you were me?

219
00:12:26,240 --> 00:12:28,000
If I were you, I would definitely go.

220
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:29,800
Why should I make it easy for him?

221
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:31,480
It's not easy for my parents to support me.

222
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:32,440
My parents won't have to pay for it,

223
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:33,680
if someone else will.

224
00:12:34,240 --> 00:12:36,970
They can spend the money on improving their life.

225
00:12:37,760 --> 00:12:38,800
As for me,

226
00:12:39,120 --> 00:12:41,080
my heart will always be with them.

227
00:12:41,480 --> 00:12:43,080
And when I complete my studies,

228
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:44,010
I will come back.

229
00:12:46,080 --> 00:12:46,880
You're right.

230
00:12:47,160 --> 00:12:47,760
My dad

231
00:12:47,760 --> 00:12:49,280
has a motto.

232
00:12:49,360 --> 00:12:50,040
There's no need

233
00:12:50,040 --> 00:12:51,170
to take the hard way.

234
00:12:52,320 --> 00:12:53,180
Think about it.

235
00:12:53,320 --> 00:12:53,800
Really.

236
00:12:55,280 --> 00:12:56,000
Right now, I just feel

237
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:57,280
that life is hard.

238
00:12:59,640 --> 00:13:00,570
What do you mean?

239
00:13:01,400 --> 00:13:02,320
It means

240
00:13:03,280 --> 00:13:05,280
that when you think things will go bad,

241
00:13:05,280 --> 00:13:06,280
it will go bad.

242
00:13:07,280 --> 00:13:08,080
You're just

243
00:13:08,080 --> 00:13:08,720
affected by

244
00:13:08,720 --> 00:13:09,320
what happened

245
00:13:09,320 --> 00:13:10,080
to Ling Xiao.

246
00:13:10,160 --> 00:13:11,080
But what happened to them

247
00:13:11,080 --> 00:13:12,340
is very rare after all.

248
00:13:12,840 --> 00:13:15,100
I think what happened to you is very rare.

249
00:13:15,120 --> 00:13:16,560
Your life has been smooth since your childhood,

250
00:13:16,560 --> 00:13:17,720
so you can be so positive

251
00:13:17,720 --> 00:13:19,450
about everything in your life.

252
00:13:20,440 --> 00:13:22,160
It can't be helped.

253
00:13:22,600 --> 00:13:23,640
I'm just so lucky.

254
00:13:24,720 --> 00:13:25,650
Well, lucky one,

255
00:13:26,840 --> 00:13:28,240
let's continue playing.

256
00:13:32,720 --> 00:13:33,360
Ma'am,

257
00:13:35,200 --> 00:13:36,130
my condolences.

258
00:13:37,760 --> 00:13:38,490
Grandma Qin,

259
00:13:39,240 --> 00:13:40,170
