282
00:14:24,600 --> 00:14:26,330
No one can take care of you here.

283
00:14:26,520 --> 00:14:27,360
I don't care!

284
00:14:27,360 --> 00:14:28,920
I don't want to leave my brother!

285
00:14:28,920 --> 00:14:30,200
I want to be here with my brother

286
00:14:30,200 --> 00:14:31,120
